------------------------------------------------------------

To reach the upper layers, the following breakthroughs are needed:

- Long‑term memory systems
- Stable multi‑agent coordination
- World‑model compression
- Self‑evaluation loops
- Distributed cognition frameworks
- Safe recursive self‑improvement
- New compute architectures

